snippet.title: Legends of Crystal | Launch Trailer | GingerSun Games
snippet.description:
Legends of Crystal is a turn-based RPG that it tells the story of a child chosen by a god who must save a crystal from evil. The crystal is divided into 6 powers due to the greed of jinns and mythical creatures in the past.

Wishlist and Try the Demo on Steam: 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1765090/Legends_of_Crystal/
